text: The 1946 Idaho gubernatorial election was held on November 5, 1946. Republican nominee C. A. Robins defeated Democratic incumbent Arnold Williams with 56.37% of the vote. ==General election== ===Candidates=== *C. A. Robins, Republican *Arnold Williams, Democratic ===Results=== ==References== 1946 Idaho Gubernatorial
title: 1946 Idaho gubernatorial election
